Bayibuli erina buli kyeweetaaga okuba n'obulamu obulungi mu Kristu.
English
Omubiri guno oguwereddwa ekitiibwa era ogugattidwa wamu n'omwoyo era nemeeme gubeera gwa mukkiriza emirembe gyonna mu Ggulu n'ensi empya (Okubikkulilwa 21-22).
Era onkoowoolenga ku lunaku olw'okulaba ennaku; Ndikuwonya, naawe olingulumiza nze!
Ekizaalibwa omubiri kiba mubiri; n'ekizaalibwa Omwoyo kiba mwoyo.
Yesu, si omu ku byetulina okulondako, Ye gwetulina okulonda yekka.
